---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
import Link from "./ui/Link.astro";
---

<Container>
  <main class="grid place-items-center gap-10 pt-16 pb-8 md:pt-12 md:pb-24 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="order-2 w-full py-4 lg:order-1">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3">
          <div class="flex gap-2" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span>
            <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></span>
            <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">
            AOS Console
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-5 py-5 md:px-6">
          <p class="font-mono text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">
            Overview
          </p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 font-sans text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950 md:text-3xl">
            从总览先下钻，再做处理动作
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
            主控台先回答当前环境是否健康，再把你带到组件、风险和处理记录，不让上下文断掉。
          </p>
        </div>

        <img
          src="/assets/dashboard.png"
          alt="Agents-of-Shield dashboard overview"
          class="w-full object-cover object-top"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
      <h1 class="max-w-[10ch] font-display text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-950 md:text-6xl xl:text-7xl">
        Local agent security, made readable.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg text-slate-500">
        Agents-of-Shield 是面向本地 AI Agent 生态的桌面安全控制台。它会发现并扫描
        Skills、MCP Servers、Tools、Prompts 与 Plugins，把原本分散且不可见的风险，整理成一套可查看、可分析、可隔离的工作流。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <Link href="#launch" class="flex items-center justify-center">
          Book Demo
        </Link>
        <Link
          size="lg"
          style="outline"
          href="#screens"
          class="flex items-center justify-center"
        >
          View Screens
        </Link>
      </div>

      <ul class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></span>
          <span>不是让 Agent 更强，而是让 Agent Runtime 更可见、更可控。</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></span>
          <span>重点回答谁被安装、具备哪些能力、又可能带来哪些风险。</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></span>
          <span>从发现到隔离都留在一个桌面入口，不打断安全判断路径。</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</Container>
